&lt;figure  id=&#34;figure-average-streamwise-velocity-as-a-function-of-the-wall-normal-distance-for-a-mathrmst--6-and-b-mathrmst--30-at-various-mass-loadings-the-solid-black-line-represents-the-particle-free-channel-darker-symbols-correspond-to-larger-mass-loadings-which-vary-from-02-10&#34;&gt;
