&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Top-down view of pseudocolor of Particle volume fraction near the wall for $\mathrm{St}^+ = 30$. We observe long streaks of particles (i.e. &amp;ldquo;ropes&amp;rdquo;) near the wall which remain stable for long periods of time.











  





